You can banish 1 Dragon-Type monster and 1 Wyrm-Type monster from your Graveyard; Special Summon 1 "Xyz-Ray Pierce" from your hand or Deck. If this card is sent from the field to the Graveyard: You can inflict 500 damage to your opponent. You can only use each effect of "Xyz-Ray Pierce" once per turn.
